  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>フラムベルクさんとの約束、
果たせなかった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We couldn't fulfill our promise with Flamberge...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>このまま、オレら、
お宝泥棒の濡れ衣かぶったままかよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now she really will think we were the thieves...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>彼女はふたりが盗んだんじゃない
ってわかってんじゃないかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't think she'll have a problem believing you aren't the thieves.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　そうなの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What? Why do you think that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41084</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの時、フラムベルクは
『不凍の流体』の話してたでしょ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At that time she talked about the Unfreezable Liquid, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>盗んだ相手にもうひとつの宝物のありかを
教えたりするかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She wouldn't have told how to get the remaining object if she truly believed you were the thieves.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、やっぱり</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're right!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だったら、そう言ってくれりゃ
よかったのに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You say that but it's not like we're off the hook...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>言ったら、君たちが『不燃の古木』を
取り返してくれないもん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you think about it, she probably never thought you'd bring back the Unburnable Tree.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_092_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレら、
都合よく利用されたのかよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I feel they've been using us all this time...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
